  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: ff8241ca5be3246e5997f9cdb47b0c7a, type: 3}
  m_Name: Training Not Started
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  _lines:
  - Everyone would be nervous when they get their first cat. Don't worry, I will
    tell you what to do!
  - 'I will give you two tasks. If you don''t finish the two quests well, you might
    lose her. '
  - 'The most important thing we have to do when raising a cat is to feed her. Now
    go to your cat and grab the food next to her. '
  - 'After she enjoys her food, come back to me for the second task! '
  _speakerName: Clerk
  hasChoice: 0
